This project aims to develop a web-based application to assist users in planning multi-
destination vacations. The application will allow users to input locations, generate optimized
routes and view detailed information about each location. Key features include efficient route
planning, location suggestions and mobile compatibility. The goal is to simplify the vacation
planning process and provide users with personalized recommendations.
Flask framework for building the web application
Travelling salesperson algorithm to calculate the most efficient routes
APIs to access and process location data using OpenStreetMap API
Creating a user-friendly interface for inputting locations, viewing
routes and interacting with the map
Implementing mechanisms to handle potential errors during data
Representing locations, routes and other relevant data
Ensuring the application is compatible with mobile devices
